data.description: Introducing this splendid detached house, boasting a multitude of impressive features. Enjoy the spacious yard, perfect for entertainment, along with a generously sized driveway capable of accommodating multiple cars.  On the first floor, you'll discover two bedrooms and a full bathroom. The  spacious finished basement is equipped with a newer washer and dryer, as well as an additional full bath for added convenience.  Moving up to the third level, you'll find a spacious main room with a full bathroom, along with a second bedroom.  This home provides central heating and air conditioning, along with the added benefit of new windows and doors. Both the electrical and heating systems have been updated within the last five years, and ceiling fans are thoughtfully placed throughout the property.  The kitchen is a true highlight, featuring state-of-the-art appliances, including an A.I refrigerator, a new stove, microwave, and dishwasher. Additionally, the kitchen boasts new cabinets, an inviting island, and fresh flooring and walls, creating a modern and inviting space for culinary endeavors. Developers Opportunity:  (Public record address 4414 Wingate & mailing address 4418 for anyone driving by)
